data.description:
Welcome Home, located in the quaint Town of DeBeque this half duplex is within walking distance to the Restaurant, Store, Beauty Salon, Parks and School. It's just a short drive to the Wild Horse area. With 1,734 sq.ft. there is room to stretch and enjoy the quiet living. 

The main floor features an open concept living, dining and kitchen area. The kitchen is great for the home chef with its ample counter space, numerous cabinets and large pantry. The powder room is conveniently located and talk about storage, this unit has plenty.

Upstairs is the owner's extra big bedroom with en-suite bath, dual separate vanities and huge walk-in closet. The two additional bedrooms are good sized and the hall located laundry area mean no lugging clothing up and down the stairs.
